## Dependency License Compatibility

This project's tools and scripts integrate with or wrap the following
open-source components. The dual-license structure is chosen to remain
compatible with all of them:

| Dependency | License | Compatible with AGPLv3 | Compatible with MIT |
|---|---|---|---|
| Ollama | MIT | ✓ | ✓ |
| Open WebUI | BSD-3-Clause | ✓ | ✓ |
| jsonallen/perplexity-mcp | MIT | ✓ (MIT branch) | ✓ |
| llama.cpp | MIT | ✓ | ✓ |
| Python requests / httpx | Apache-2.0 | ✓ | ✓ |
| Docker Compose | Apache-2.0 | ✓ | ✓ |
| bootstrap-foundation (upstream) | AGPL-3.0 OR MIT | ✓ | ✓ |

**Note on AGPL propagation:** This project wraps external services
(Ollama, Open WebUI) as separate processes via Docker/HTTP. Wrapper
shell scripts and Python tools in this repo do NOT create a combined
work with those services under AGPL copyleft rules — they communicate
over standard network interfaces. You are not required to open-source
Ollama or Open WebUI modifications to use this repo under AGPLv3.

