## Choose your license

| | Community | Developer |
|---|---|---|
| **License** | AGPLv3 | MIT |
| **Cost** | Free | Free |
| **Open-Source projects** | ✓ | ✓ |
| **Commercial use** | Only if source is open | ✓ Yes |
| **SaaS / Network services** | Only if source is open | ✓ Yes |
| **Closed-Source** | ✗ | ✓ Yes |
| **Source disclosure** | Required | Not required |

**Rule of thumb:**
- Open-source project or internal tool → **AGPLv3**
- Commercial software, SaaS, Closed-Source → **MIT**
- Enterprise deployment or support wanted → office@greev.com

